{"tid":1433771,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有個朋友過咗身仲未平伏到心情","createTime":"2019-08-08T14:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T02:19:44.000Z","uid":175661,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dd8d2848b9b2a874b9f371b50986e7117b3979cf","tid":1433771,"uid":175661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:44:01.000Z","msg":"呢位朋友都係連登認識 佢大過我好幾年 <br />\n知我獨家村冇朋友願意同我做朋友 佢真係好好人對我好好<br />\n但佢一直都有情緒問題 我好努力陪佢度過希望佢會好返但我做唔到<br />\n佢情況最壞嗰時已經成日唔應機好難搵到佢<br />\n有次佢突然搵我送禮物畀我我都已經心知不妙<br />\n最後真係發生咗<br />\n<br />\n我心情到而家都未好得返晒 覺得自己做得唔夠<br />\n成日諗如果再捉緊啲睇實啲會唔會冇事<br />\n唔知點解有好大失落感 個心好空虛嘅感覺<br />\n我可以做啲咩先可以平伏?"},{"pid":"85f902198cd8d52cb8c20bf475ba60111333c252","tid":1433771,"uid":150348,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:45:08.000Z","msg":"唯有時間可以撫平傷口"},{"pid":"38c3d7bd57864e493401ec29d8e61a0ba9f72a57","tid":1433771,"uid":258513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:08:04.000Z","msg":"得時間可以治療到 巴打加油"},{"pid":"dcf6c6cfeff969cee1076a009209228dbb9d814b","tid":1433771,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1e13d61f05189ec78d659ef81fba730d3555c1","tid":1433771,"uid":144556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:10:02.000Z","msg":"時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前中學miss係靠信仰"},{"pid":"af846b291513970c089907b76041eeae8a059443","tid":1433771,"uid":208891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:15:11.000Z","msg":"振作呀 佢有冇講過有啲咩係特別想做架 你帶住佢既精神去幫佢完成"},{"pid":"f8